{"tid":2342550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鮑威爾 270頁報告證外國干預美國大選 , 建議總統動用 IEEPA","createTime":"2020-12-27T08:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T13:48:48.000Z","uid":25468,"like":300,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"97a035687fdd230d6eda64c3d362214c78f2e387","tid":2342550,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2020/12/attorney-sidney-attorney-sidney-powell-releases-270-page-document-on-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign-interference-releases-270-page-document-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatewaypundit.com%2F2020%2F12%2Fattorney-sidney-attorney-sidney-powell-releases-270-page-document-on-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign-interference-releases-270-page-document-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=f6002ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2020/12/attorney-sidney-attorney-sidney-powell-releases-270-page-document-on-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign-interference-releases-270-page-document-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign/</a><br />\n<br />\nIEEPA 國際緊急經濟權力法<br />\n<br />\n國際緊急經濟權力法（英語：International Emergency Economic Powers Act，IEEPA，Title II of 美國聯邦公法第95&ndash;223號，91 Stat. 1626，1977年10月28日頒布），是一項美國聯邦法律，授權總統宣布國家緊急狀態後規範商業的權力，以應對外國的任何異常狀況或特殊威脅[1]。該法案於1977年12月28日由美國第95屆國會會議通過，並由吉米&middot;卡特總統簽署[2]。2018－2019年中美貿易戰期間，美國總統川普稱將援引該法要求駐華企業離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n* 簡單啲講 , 可以凍結相關國家及國內勾結組織或人員所有美元資產<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%B4%A7%E6%80%A5%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%9D%83%E5%8A%9B%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259B%25BD%25E9%2599%2585%25E7%25B4%25A7%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%25BB%258F%25E6%25B5%258E%25E6%259D%2583%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%25B3%2595&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=82146486\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%B4%A7%E6%80%A5%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%9D%83%E5%8A%9B%E6%B3%95</a>"},{"pid":"e3b242f525b72eb027872811e972dadc2639db37","tid":2342550,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:21:08.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e23db4ec9abeace41deecf7e6bef95d29e085b93","tid":2342550,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5150535d9a2a5fce181cabca5d646c422cfdd085","tid":2342550,"uid":47356,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"Sir Do It!"},{"pid":"7cfb004a670d989940dcd5d642e673ed4c62cc55","tid":2342550,"uid":337826,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"主流媒體看不到的新聞<br />\n然後啲人就問證據呢"},{"pid":"c033a82eeebf34bda5671395954f1b979c638d1d","tid":2342550,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7315e8fd458ebbc7ea0cc199b23c6d3d07fc126c","tid":2342550,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">侵侵要贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8564ae1260aadd913a40e5510c6f23f485053f86","tid":2342550,"uid":200280,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"7cfb004a670d989940dcd5d642e673ed4c62cc55","tid":2342550,"uid":337826,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"c