lection-fraud-involving-foreign-interference-releases-270-page-document-massive-2020-election-fraud-involving-foreign/</a><br />\n<br />\nIEEPA 國際緊急經濟權力法<br />\n<br />\n國際緊急經濟權力法（英語：International Emergency Economic Powers Act，IEEPA，Title II of 美國聯邦公法第95&ndash;223號，91 Stat. 1626，1977年10月28日頒布），是一項美國聯邦法律，授權總統宣布國家緊急狀態後規範商業的權力，以應對外國的任何異常狀況或特殊威脅[1]。該法案於1977年12月28日由美國第95屆國會會議通過，並由吉米&middot;卡特總統簽署[2]。2018－2019年中美貿易戰期間，美國總統川普稱將援引該法要求駐華企業離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n* 簡單啲講 , 可以凍結相關國家及國內勾結組織或人員所有美元資產<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%B4%A7%E6%80%A5%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%9D%83%E5%8A%9B%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259B%25BD%25E9%2599%2585%25E7%25B4%25A7%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%25BB%258F%25E6%25B5%258E%25E6%259D%2583%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%25B3%2595&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=82146486\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%B4%A7%E6%80%A5%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%9D%83%E5%8A%9B%E6%B3%95</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"呢個post好多留言都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9013522bbf4b9fdef9bb698bb685cd24c2960af7","tid":2342550,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba5582fc4c17360d8945aa7068baa2eb75b6621","tid":2342550,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c1b2c39689be6190795ae3e2c87cfd31d85e3b","tid":2342550,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score